title: Grateful Dead Live at Great Western LA Forum on 1989-02-10
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Franklin's Tower-> Walkin' Blues, To Lay Me Down, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Friend Of The Devil, Let It Grow

Set 2

A Little Light, Truckin'-> Crazy Fingers, Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Wharf Rat, Sugar Magnolia, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

reviews.review_text: Nice show, nice sound Very nice  show.  Lots of jamming. Good FOB recording.  better than the other Schoeps version. The Truckin Crazy Playin is great.  Playin is even better than the very good version on 2/5 in Oakland.  Let it Grow sets the tone for the upcoming set 2.
